# RUN: %pyxc < %s 2>&1 | FileCheck %s
# CHECK: Evaluated to 14.000000
# CHECK: Evaluated to 7.000000


# Tests: operator precedence (* > +) and left-associativity of -.
# binoprhs = { binaryop unaryexpr }
#
# 2 + 3 * 4 = 2 + 12 = 14  (not (2+3)*4 = 20)
# 10 - 2 - 1 = (10-2) - 1 = 7  (not 10 - (2-1) = 9, confirming left-assoc)

2 + 3 * 4

10 - 2 - 1
